These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, sprite, 7up, tea
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, snowboarding, lacrosse, climbing
1. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##5
2. the person drinking sprite is not the person who's sport is skiing##6
3. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
4. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
6. the person who's sport is skiing is not the person drinking 7up##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | sprite   | tea    | cola    | 7up |
| Sport      | climbing | skiing | lacrosse | snowboarding |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, lemonade, water, tea
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, cauliflower, zucchini, cranberry
1. the person eating eggplant is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
3. the person eating cranberry is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5
4. the person drinking lemonade is not the person eating cauliflower##6
5. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person drinking water##1
6. the person eating eggplant is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1
7. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
8. the person drinking water is somewhere to the left of the person drinking 7up##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | lemonade  | water    | 7up | tea    |
| Food       | cranberry | cauliflower | zucchini  | eggplant |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, tea, almond-milk, milk
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, software-developer, writer, scientist
1. the person drinking milk is not the fisherman##6
2. the software-developer is not the person drinking almond-milk##6
3. the writer is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
4. the software-developer is the person drinking juice##1
5. the person drinking tea is on the left of the software-developer##1
6. the person drinking juice is in an odd position##4
7. the fisherman is on the far left or far right##3
8. the writer is somewhere to the left of the scientist##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | milk       | tea  | juice  | almond-milk |
| Job        | writer | scientist | software-developer | fisherman  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-4::.
4 different pets are kept: pony, turtle, hamster, chinchilla
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, scooter, van, airplane
1. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
2. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the left of the person driving the snowmobile##5
3. the person driving the airplane is not the owner of the turtle##6
4. the person driving the airplane is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5
5. the person driving the van is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
6. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the left of the person driving the airplane##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |    4     |
| Pet         | turtle | hamster | chinchilla     | pony |
| Transport   | scooter     | van    | snowmobile | airplane    |

