.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, almond-milk, hot-chocolate, soy-milk
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, taxi, train, skateboard
1. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the left of the person driving the train##5
3. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the left of the person driving the taxi##5
4. the person drinking almond-milk is not the person driving the skateboard##6
5. the person driving the motorbike is not the person drinking cola##6
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
7. the person driving the train is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | cola        | soy-milk | hot-chocolate | almond-milk |
| Transport   | skateboard | motorbike | taxi     | train   |

