.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, sports, musical, animation
There are 4 different nationalities: british, brazilian, german, nigerian
1. the british is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
2. the person watching animation movies is not the brazilian##6
3. the british is on the far right##1
4. the brazilian is somewhere to the right of the nigerian##5
5. the person watching musical movies is the person watching musical movies##1
6. the person watching musical movies is somewhere to the left of the british##5
7. the person watching musical movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##5
8. the person watching sports movies is somewhere to the left of the nigerian##5
9. the person watching sports movies is somewhere to the left of the nigerian##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | musical    | martial-arts  | animation   |
| Nationality   | german  | nigerian | brazilian | british |

