.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, epic, action, comedy
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, trance, techno, classical
1. the fan techno is on the left or right of the fan metal##3
2. the fan techno is not the person watching epic movies##6
3. the person watching scientific movies is the fan trance##1
4. the fan metal is on the left or right of the fan classical##3
5. the fan techno is on the far left##1
6. the person watching epic movies is the fan metal##1
7. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the left of the fan metal##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |      3      |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | epic     | action | scientific |
| Music-Genre   | techno | metal | classical      | trance         |

