3. the chef is on the right of the software-developer##1
4. the software-developer is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
5. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the software-developer##3
6. the firefighter is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
7. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the right of the person drinking sprite##5
8. the person drinking juice is not the chef##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Beverage   | juice  | coffee        | sprite      | cola          |
| Job        | firefighter | software-developer | chef | fisherman |

