.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, scientist, mechanic, musician
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, roller, bike, taxi
1. the accountant is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the roller is not the musician##6
3. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the right of the mechanic##5
4. the person driving the taxi is in an even position##4
5. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
6. the person driving the taxi is the mechanic##1
7. the accountant is not the person driving the taxi##6
8. the scientist is somewhere to the right of the musician##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Job         | accountant  | mechanic | musician    | scientist |
| Transport   | roller | taxi | bike | trike  |

