.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-10::.
4 different pets are kept: pony, mouse, guinea-pig, frog
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, snowboarding, parkour, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is cycling is not the owner of the pony##6
2. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
3. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
4. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
5. the owner of the guinea-pig is not the person who's sport is volleyball##6
6. the person who's sport is snowboarding is not the owner of the mouse##6
7. the person who's sport is volleyball is in an even position##4
8. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person who's sport is cycling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4     |
| Pet     | guinea-pig | pony        | frog  | mouse     |
| Sport   | cycling     | volleyball | snowboarding | parkour |

