.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, video-games, collecting, writing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, dubstep, reggae, country
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3
2. the fan dubstep is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##5
3. the fan reggae is not the person who's hobby is collecting##6
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is between the fan country and the person who's hobby is collecting##2
5. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
6. the fan dubstep is between the fan folk and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |   3   |     4     |
| Hobby         | collecting | video-games    | magic-tricks | writing |
| Music-Genre   | folk         | dubstep | country   | reggae     |

