.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-12::.
There 4 different types of food: raspberry, avocado, pineapple, grapefruit
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, train, tram, airplane
1. the person eating pineapple is somewhere to the right of the person driving the tram##5
2. the person eating grapefruit is not the person driving the roller##6
3. the person driving the train is the person eating grapefruit##1
4. the person driving the train is on the right of the person eating avocado##1
5. the person driving the tram is not the person eating grapefruit##6
6. the person eating avocado is not the person driving the roller##6
7. the person eating pineapple is somewhere to the left of the person eating avocado##5
8. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |   4    |
| Food        | raspberry  | pineapple | avocado | grapefruit |
| Transport   | tram | roller     | airplane     | train    |

