3. the person eating watermelon is the person watching satire movies##1
4. the person eating peach is somewhere to the right of the person watching spy movies##5
5. the person eating watermelon is between the person eating grapes and the person watching musical movies##2
6. the person eating grapes is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | avocado | grapes      | watermelon | peach   |
| Movie-Genre   | spy     | mystery | satire   | musical |

