1. the person watching thriller movies is not the person drinking almond-milk##6
2. the person watching thriller movies is the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the person watching spy movies is between the person drinking mirinda and the person drinking iced-tea##2
4. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
5. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3     |      4       |
| Beverage      | almond-milk       | iced-tea | soy-milk     | mirinda     |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | thriller       | spy | musical |

