5. the person who's sport is golf is between the police-officer and the person who's sport is snowboarding##2
6. the police-officer is not the person who's sport is basketball##6
7. the pilot is on the right of the project-manager##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Job     | designer  | project-manager | pilot | police-officer |
| Sport   | basketball | snowboarding | golf   | tennis |

