.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-19::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, filmmaking, drawing, gardening
4 different pets are kept: horse, ferret, goat, goldfish
1. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goat##5
2. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the right of the owner of the ferret##5
3. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
4. the owner of the goldfish is not the person who's hobby is collecting##6
5. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##2
6. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
8. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the right of the owner of the ferret##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | drawing | collecting | gardening |
| Pet     | goat  | ferret      | horse  | goldfish       |

